<title>USA: Macromedia says hit with class-action suit.</title>
<headline>Macromedia says hit with class-action suit.</headline>
<dateline>SAN FRANCISCO 1997-08-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Macromedia Inc said a securities class-action lawsuit has been filed against it and certain of its officers in the California Superior Court in San Francisco.</p>
<p>The suit was filed on behalf of all persons who bought Macromedia's common stock from April 18, 1996 through January 9, 1997, the company said in a statement.</p>
<p>The company said it has not yet been served with the lawsuit, which it intends to fight vigorously.</p>
